{
  "stem": "17001.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when it quieted down a little, the [GERMAN] says that when we came in, there was a little teeny window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the skinniest girl should come over and we will clean the debris from the window and climb through, and go and ask for help.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you have to speak German or some other language, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So luckily, this little skinny girl, she climbed through the window and she went and there were French and Italian prisoners who were working there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then she told them that come and help to clean the doorway so that these girls could come out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They said, oh, there must be Germans and they send you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We don't-- we not going to rescue no Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "These are all my kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "These are all half-lings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they came, and they made a little opening at the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The minute we walked out, the 60 of us, the whole building collapsed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When-- when somebody wanted to-- the [GERMAN] said go back and get the [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were no more-- no more where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then we started to march home--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the Simmons factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Simmons factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then as we were going home, the electric wires were all over on the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to watch it that you shouldn't step on the live wire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we get to near to the railway station, the bridge that was the overpass was holes on it that you didn't know if you going to fell into it or you were able to go on that teeny little narrow ledge that was left over.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was a-- a nightmare, how we got back to our lager.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
